name: The Daily Good 18.3.22
description:
Our stories give life meaning.

New stories, old stories, true stories of our lives and fictional stories of made-up lands with characters born of imagination.

Some stories we tell over and over, others we hope no one ever hears.

Our stories are what carry us on through the ages, long after we've breathed our last breath.

What are the stories that make up your life?
And are they good?
